WEBVTT

00:03.394 --> 00:05.092
PERSON:
Previously onFuture Man:

00:05.266 --> 00:06.745
SUSAN:
Haven does not exist
in time or space.

00:06.919 --> 00:09.313
The only way to put it on a map
is from the inside,

00:09.487 --> 00:12.142
and that's exactly what these
geolocation devices will do.

00:12.316 --> 00:13.535
Look who's here.

00:13.709 --> 00:15.798
Oh, savior,
back from the dead.

00:15.972 --> 00:17.626
They think that
I'm Nut-Face Josh.

