[SHOUTS]
I'm Nut-Face Josh now?

00:19.454 --> 00:20.890
You've got status here.

00:21.064 --> 00:22.979
Use that to get
a proper lay of the land.

00:23.153 --> 00:24.981
Hey, sad boy.
You okay?

00:25.155 --> 00:27.027
Was Marilyn Monroe
just hitting on you?

00:27.201 --> 00:28.376
Give me answers.

00:28.550 --> 00:30.117
You must go
to the enchanted meadow.

00:30.291 --> 00:31.422
TIGER:
Who's up there?

00:31.596 --> 00:32.771
GANDHI:
Greatest of all time.

00:32.945 --> 00:34.425
WOLF:
Something's off here.

00:34.599 --> 00:35.992
