all the time.

01:22.473 --> 01:24.954
"Everything feels like a dream.

01:25.128 --> 01:27.652
Better than a dream.
Like magic."

01:27.826 --> 01:28.784
♪ Every day ♪

01:28.958 --> 01:31.656
Yes, whoo!

01:31.830 --> 01:35.269
♪ Going faster
Than a roller coaster ♪

01:35.443 --> 01:39.838
What spell have you cast
on me, Goat-Wizard?

01:40.012 --> 01:42.145
♪ A-hey, a-hey, hey ♪

01:42.319 --> 01:45.061
Ever since I met you,
I can't stop thinking.

01:45.235 --> 01:48.238
Think, think.
Why doesn't it move?

01:48.412 --> 01:52.155
We don't have all time.
We have no time.

01:52.329 --> 01:53.461
No time at all.

01:56.551 --> 01:57.769
♪ Every day ♪

01:57.943 --> 02:00.250
Wait, James, come back here!

02:00.424 --> 02:01.947
Let me yell in your face
some more

02:02.122 --> 02:03.688
about how this place
is fucked up!

02:03.862 --> 02:05.864
JOSH:
"This place is paradise.

02:06.038 --> 02:08.215
"Always 74 and glow-y,

02:08.389 --> 02:10.173
"the hint of a breeze,

02:10.347 --> 02:13.045
filled with amazing people
you can talk to forever."

02:13.220 --> 02:15.309
TIGER:
I don't talk. I act.

02:15.483 --> 02:17.485
I kill,
you two-horned fuck.

02:17.659 --> 02:19.748
That's what I'm going back
to the sewer to do.

02:19.922 --> 02:22.620
What do you mean,
I-- I never left the sewer?

02:22.794 --> 02:25.667
Of course I did.
I'm here, aren't I?

02:28.496 --> 02:31.977
Unless-- Unless I--

02:32.152 --> 02:35.764
I bring the sewer with me
wherever I go.

02:35.938 --> 02:37.461
[BELL JANGLES]

02:37.635 --> 02:38.854
[GROANS]

02:39.028 --> 02:40.595
I gotta lie down.
I'm gonna lie down.

02:40.769 --> 02:41.770
I gotta lie down.

02:44.033 --> 02:45.426
[SIGHS]

02:45.600 --> 02:47.471
[BREATHING HEAVILY]
I need to get up.

02:47.645 --> 02:49.038
[GROANS]

02:49.212 --> 02:50.605
I need to move.

02:50.779 --> 02:52.389
[EXHALES SHARPLY]
I need to breathe.

02:52.563 --> 02:55.000
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

02:55.175 --> 02:57.133
[GROANS]

02:57.307 --> 02:59.396
Remember what Yoko taught me:

02:59.570 --> 03:01.398
"Now is in the breathing,

03:01.572 --> 03:03.705
and Paul's a whiny
little bitch."

03:03.879 --> 03:05.533
[GROANS]
I need to remember.

03:05.707 --> 03:08.144
JOSH:  "I need to remember the smell,

03:08.318 --> 03:09.928
"the feel, the colors.

03:10.102 --> 03:12.583
"All of it perfect.
I want to write it down.

03:12.757 --> 03:13.715
Savor each memory."

03:13.889 --> 03:16.152
My earliest memory?

03:16.326 --> 03:17.893
Crawling
in a pool of blood.

03:18.067 --> 03:21.113
Pretty sure
it wasn't my own.

03:21.288 --> 03:23.290
Again with the
"How did it make you feel?"

03:23.464 --> 03:25.988
[LAUGHS]
You are relentless.

03:26.162 --> 03:28.338
I feel like
I'm making progress.

03:28.512 --> 03:30.514
I feel like I'm going
Brian Wilson!

03:30.688 --> 03:32.299
JOSH:
"I feel like I'm happy.

03:32.473 --> 03:34.388
"Truly happy
for the first time.

03:34.562 --> 03:38.043
"This is home.
Oh, look at that.

03:38.218 --> 03:39.697
"On the last page
of my journal.

03:39.871 --> 03:41.569
Guess I'll go put it
in the library."

03:41.743 --> 03:45.573
♪ My way
A-hey, a-hey, hey ♪

03:45.747 --> 03:52.232
♪ Love like yours
Will surely come my way ♪

03:52.406 --> 03:55.278
[CLOCK TICKING]

03:59.021 --> 04:01.937
[♪♪♪]

04:05.332 --> 04:08.160
[WHOOSHING]

04:11.990 --> 04:14.906
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

04:16.734 --> 04:18.606
[♪♪♪]

04:36.363 --> 04:38.103
Shut up, shut up,
shut up!

04:38.278 --> 04:39.670
How are we supposed

04:39.844 --> 04:41.672
to talk through our problems
if you keep--

04:41.846 --> 04:42.891
We don't have
a problem.

04:43.065 --> 04:44.980
You have a problem
with me.

04:45.154 --> 04:46.460
No, no! I-- I just--

04:46.634 --> 04:49.071
Marilyn,
you are so much more

04:49.245 --> 04:51.726
than this horny-all-the-time
sex goddess.

04:51.900 --> 04:54.990
I just want you to become
the fullest version of yourself,

04:55.164 --> 04:56.644
and I wanna help you to grow.

04:56.818 --> 04:59.821
Stop trying to fix me!Oh, please!

04:59.995 --> 05:01.562
