Weren't you married?Yeah, to the teth-life.

09:00.801 --> 09:02.498
This is the only ball
and chain I'll ever need.

09:02.672 --> 09:04.587
Yeah, I know how much
you love tetherball.

09:04.761 --> 09:06.676
Shit, he's walking over.
Avoid eye contact.

09:06.850 --> 09:08.156
Who?

09:08.330 --> 09:09.679
Fuck, fuck, fuck.
He saw me.

09:09.853 --> 09:11.899
This is why you gotta
rock shades, brah.

09:12.073 --> 09:13.857
[♪♪♪]

09:15.337 --> 09:16.904
I just wanted
to give you your hat.

09:18.514 --> 09:19.950
Take your hat back, man!

09:20.124 --> 09:21.691
That ain't my hat.
I'm a Kangol man.

09:21.865 --> 09:22.910
Always have been,
always will be.

09:23.084 --> 09:25.042
No, no!
You wear this hat!

09:25.216 --> 09:26.261
[LAUGHS]

09:26.435 --> 09:27.784
That's
ridiculous.

09:27.958 --> 09:29.264
That's a magician's hat,
not a teth-baller's.

09:29.438 --> 09:31.658
No, you're wrong.
I remember!

09:31.832 --> 09:34.965
I remember!
Uh, sort of.

09:35.139 --> 09:37.272
[SNIFFLING]
Memory works different here.

09:37.446 --> 09:38.839
It-- It's fleeting.

09:39.013 --> 09:41.406
Slides away unless you know
how to hold on.

09:41.581 --> 09:43.974
[BREATHING DEEPLY AND GROANING]

09:44.148 --> 09:45.715
Okay, hey, hey, hey,
hey, hey, look.

09:45.889 --> 09:47.369
Just take it easy,
all right?

09:47.543 --> 09:49.501
We're-we're having a nice day,
the sun's out--

09:49.676 --> 09:51.199
The sun's always out!

09:51.373 --> 09:53.767
The sun's always out and
there's no way to mark time.

09:53.941 --> 09:56.030
