It's just day to night.

09:56.204 --> 09:59.555
Aging, seasons,
just slips away.

09:59.729 --> 10:01.209
[EXHALES SHARPLY]

10:01.383 --> 10:03.341
You have the memory of
a goldfish, man!

10:03.515 --> 10:04.865
