[GOAT BLEATING]

12:16.605 --> 12:18.041
No, no, thank you.

12:18.215 --> 12:20.174
I mean, this has been
a journey inward.

12:20.348 --> 12:24.874
Yeah, it was--
It was painful at first.

12:26.746 --> 12:30.619
