12:39.933 --> 12:41.543
No, okay, okay, okay.

12:41.717 --> 12:44.938
You know that when you
get mysterious and aloof,

12:45.112 --> 12:48.071
it triggers-- It triggers
my feelings of abandonment

12:48.245 --> 12:50.770
from my absent par--
Goddamn it.

12:50.944 --> 12:54.295
Okay, what am I supposed
to do with all of these?

12:54.469 --> 12:57.037
I mean, can you at least
give me a little hint?

12:57.211 --> 12:58.995
Hmm?

12:59.169 --> 13:01.389
Boy, you were a real
Chatty Cathy up on the hill,

13:01.563 --> 13:02.825
and now, what,
you're just--

13:02.999 --> 13:04.479
You're gonna take
a vow of silence?

13:04.653 --> 13:06.829
I mean, that--
Heh, heh.

13:07.003 --> 13:10.224
That's rich.
That is rich.

13:11.834 --> 13:12.704
Well, thank you.

13:12.879 --> 13:14.794
I mean, was that so hard?

13:14.968 --> 13:16.578
Okay, so I got to, uh...

13:17.797 --> 13:20.843
Uh, find balance.

13:21.017 --> 13:22.323
The fuck does that mean?

13:22.497 --> 13:24.368
[♪♪♪]

13:32.333 --> 13:34.291
If I balance these rocks,

13:34.465 --> 13:36.728
I balance myself.

13:36.903 --> 13:38.513
I see where your head's at,
goat.

13:38.687 --> 13:40.820
All right, let's do this.

13:40.994 --> 13:42.038
Okay.

13:42.212 --> 13:43.779
Let's get this bad boy.

13:43.953 --> 13:47.652
[GRUNTING]

13:49.437 --> 13:50.481
Okay.

